    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to see any other way out. doctors won't do anything, the meds don't work... it feels like i'm just trapped in this body. you talk about letting go like it's something that makes sense, but it's so scary to even think about. do you really think there's any real mercy in just... stopping?",
